{"tid":2014427,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭月娥63歲生日   杜汶澤 : 遺臭萬年","createTime":"2020-05-13T04:34:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-13T04:58:51.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b6da284d620f2c07622bd99f5f0edc3fbe77ad08","tid":2014427,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T04:34:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2020/05/13/phpXEiG1m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2020%2F05%2F13%2FphpXEiG1m.jpg&h=4fac82e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（彭博）<br />\n<br />\n香港「反送中」將滿一週年，各地反送中行動至今仍未停歇，特首林鄭月娥成了眾矢之的，港星杜汶澤今（13）日上午開第一槍痛斥過生日的林鄭月娥將會遺臭萬年。<br />\n<br />\n今天是林鄭63歲生日，杜汶澤透過臉書公開嗆她：「63年前的今天，你老母把你帶到這世界，將你撫養成人，她應該未想到當日手抱的嬰兒，長大後因為樣子醜陋而產生的自卑感，導致她好勝、貪權，成為一個經常以笑遮醜，為了自尊而埋沒良知，甘為極權作奴而欺壓人民的傀儡地方首長，遺臭萬年，黃藍皆罵的老賤婦！」<br />\n<br />\n最後杜汶澤更奉勸林鄭：「生命影響生命，你的生命卻毫無半點存在價值，根本不配慶祝誕生之日；希望你早點自盡，一死以謝天下。」引發議論。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/3163848\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fent.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F3163848&d=RJ6DAKdT%2BAkj0rfdhPz9NVDApO%2Br9QW7Zx2priNtVuo%3D&h=281ae8ef\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fent.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F3163848&h=04ec523c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/3163848</a>"},{"pid":"31085decf397ac1fa5a51b7bf7d47b0549690502","tid":2014427,"uid":271199,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T04:51:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好文采"},{"pid":"80bdb4971b316d42c4e36f0c31b6e3f3d511585f","tid":2014427,"uid":342354,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T04:58:51.000Z","msg":"祝佢長命百歲，百病纏身，死唔斷氣，白頭人送黑頭人，無仔送終<br />\n<br />\n唔該Ching接力"}]}